metadata.name: Cheap Kiss Poster - Sketch
metadata.description:
This is DRAW WITH GER!  

The mechanics are simple: Starting with the sketch, you must burn this token to go forward in the creative process... and you can stop where you want!  

All burns will cost 2x of the previous token:   
Read more here: https://twitter.com/Ger_Head 

The first edition is Draw with Ger featuring Chip Kiss!  
Cheap Kiss is a trio from Barcelona playing classic Ramones-style Rock and Roll.  
Music junkies that don't take themselves too seriously except for having a good time and playing fast Punk Rock songs. Hey Ho!  
https://cheapkiss.bandcamp.com/
